import React, { useEffect } from 'react' import { Container, Progress, Row, Col } from 'reactstrap' import axios from 'axios' import { useState } from 'react' const RecAmountNutri = ({item}) => { const [min, setMin] = useState(0) const [max, setMax] = useState(0) const [unit, setUnit] = useState("") switch(item.nutri_name){ case "오메가3" : setMin(0.5) setMax(4) setUnit("g") break; case "유산균" : setMin(100000000) setMax(1000000000) setUnit("CFU") break; case "루테인" : setMin(10) setMax(20) setUnit("mg") break; case "밀크씨슬" : setMin(130) setMax(420) setUnit("mg") break; case "비타민C" : setMin(500) setMax(2000) setUnit("mg") break; case "코엔자임Q10" : setMin(90) setMax(100) setUnit("mg") break; case "보스웰리아" : setMin(100) setMax(250) setUnit("mg") break; case "글루코사민" : setMin(1.5) setMax("") setUnit("g") break; } return (
{item.nutri_name} 성인기준 일 권장량 대비 80% {item.nutri_content} 10mg 20mg
) } export default RecAmountNutri
